<distribution-code display="yes">II</distribution-code><congress>119th CONGRESS</congress><session>1st Session</session><legis-num>S. 296</legis-num><current-chamber>IN THE SENATE OF THE UNITED STATES</current-chamber><action><action-date date="20250129">January 29, 2025</action-date><action-desc><sponsor name-id="S330">Mr. Bennet</sponsor> (for himself and <cosponsor name-id="S408">Mr. Hickenlooper</cosponsor>) introduced the following bill; which was read twice and referred to the <committee-name committee-id="SSEG00">Committee on Energy and Natural Resources</committee-name></action-desc></action><legis-type>A BILL</legis-type><official-title>To make certain modifications to the repayment for the Arkansas Valley Conduit in the State of Colorado.</official-title></form><legis-body display-enacting-clause="yes-display-enacting-clause"><section section-type="section-one" id="iddf043f0415ae4554ab5c3d47ffde9f31"><enum>1.</enum><header>Short title</header><text display-inline="no-display-inline">This Act may be cited as the <quote><short-title>Finish the Arkansas Valley Conduit Act</short-title></quote>.</text></section><section commented="no" display-inline="no-display-inline" id="id7a0eac2965544e1bbaa16a0ad9e9d6ba"><enum>2.</enum><header>Arkansas Valley Conduit, Colorado</header><text display-inline="no-display-inline">Public Law 87–590 (76 Stat. 389) is amended—</text><paragraph commented="no" display-inline="no-display-inline" id="id718f7e6f59b9432db628790533bbeabe"><enum>(1)</enum><text display-inline="yes-display-inline">in subsection (c) of the first section (76 Stat. 390; 123 Stat. 1320), in the second sentence—</text><subparagraph commented="no" display-inline="no-display-inline" id="idc39eba453e48433b93048a5101650a06"><enum>(A)</enum><text display-inline="yes-display-inline">by inserting <quote>, without interest,</quote> before <quote>in an amount</quote>;</text></subparagraph><subparagraph commented="no" display-inline="no-display-inline" id="id23131362bca744ed850507ad05dda433"><enum>(B)</enum><text display-inline="yes-display-inline">by striking <quote>that is comprised of revenue generated by payments</quote> and inserting <quote>, which payment shall only consist of funding provided during construction from any person other than the Secretary</quote>; </text></subparagraph><subparagraph id="idb890550932e9444686471014a28786c7"><enum>(C)</enum><text>by inserting <quote>of</quote> before <quote>revenue that</quote>; and</text></subparagraph><subparagraph commented="no" display-inline="no-display-inline" id="ide67a0820f18247ce94276488425f7494"><enum>(D)</enum><text display-inline="yes-display-inline">by inserting <quote>over a period of 100 years</quote> after <quote>project facilities</quote>; and</text></subparagraph></paragraph><paragraph commented="no" display-inline="no-display-inline" id="id068df76706be458084aa8e37df10f852"><enum>(2)</enum><text>in section 2(b)(3)(A) (76 Stat. 390; 123 Stat. 1321)—</text><subparagraph commented="no" display-inline="no-display-inline" id="id723dbe22907b4fce9b54c2c0cba3f14e"><enum>(A)</enum><text display-inline="yes-display-inline">by striking <quote>plus interest</quote>; and</text></subparagraph><subparagraph commented="no" display-inline="no-display-inline" id="id68991370c67f4670aa0fcdf8b9d85a55"><enum>(B)</enum><text display-inline="yes-display-inline">by striking <quote>this section</quote> and inserting <quote>subsection (c) of the first section</quote>.</text></subparagraph></paragraph></section></legis-body></bill> 

